.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH plan 1  "plan " 
.SH NAME
plan \- Run the individual planning cycle (aggregate When/Which → plan; emit upward)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBplan\fR [\fB\-\-cadence\fR] [\fB\-\-need\fR] [\fB\-\-emit\fR] [\fB\-\-owner\fR] [\fB\-\-cao\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Run the individual planning cycle (aggregate When/Which → plan; emit upward)
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-cadence\fR \fI<CADENCE>\fR [default: weekly]
Cadence: weekly | monthly | yearly
.TP
\fB\-\-need\fR \fI<NEEDS>\fR
A required capability/skill package this agent needs (repeatable)
.TP
\fB\-\-emit\fR
Emit upward signals (priority ask + capability gap) over the bus
.TP
\fB\-\-owner\fR \fI<OWNER>\fR
Process/project owner address (priority ask). Else REGIN_PROCESS_OWNER
.TP
\fB\-\-cao\fR \fI<CAO>\fR
CAO address (capability gaps). Else REGIN_CAO, else cao@hq
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
